item.description:
Note: You need to run this before _any_ other request if you are using Postman.
--------------------

Add your Web Server URL, user name, base64 encoded password to the pre-request script and execute the `Environment Setup` request to setup the environment.

```
//set your CS username and password here
postman.setEnvironmentVariable("userName", "<userName>");
postman.setEnvironmentVariable("password", "<Base64 Encoded Password>");

// Set your WebService URL
postman.setEnvironmentVariable("ServerUrl", "http://MyCompany:81/SearchSvc/CVWebService.svc");
```

